So ?

341
00:20:07,290 --> 00:20:08,791
那么就取决于损坏程度有多大
So depending on the extend of the damage

342
00:20:08,791 --> 00:20:11,919
我们不能保证因此而产生的能量不反馈到别的地方
we can't rule out a catastrophic power
feed back in the drive manifolds.

343
00:20:11,919 --> 00:20:13,212
请不要用术语
Without the techno babble please.

344
00:20:13,254 --> 00:20:16,174
Cavenaugh博士, 只是想说,
有一点可能性,
Doctor Cavenaugh, was pointing out,
that there's a very slim chance,

345
00:20:16,215 --> 00:20:19,135
