00:20:21,304 --> 00:20:23,097
她的意思是爆炸
She means to say explode.

348
00:20:23,973 --> 00:20:27,310
特别是当McKay开始检查线路,
Especially if McKay starts nosing around
inside the control conduits,

349
00:20:27,393 --> 00:20:28,936
尝试整修推进器的时候
to attract the drive pod manually.

350
00:20:29,020 --> 00:20:31,230
他肯定会的. 我知道我会这么做
And he will. I know I would.

351
00:20:31,272 --> 00:20:34,233
Zelenka正在想办法
我刚刚从那里回来
Zelenka's working on simulations.
I just came from there.

352
00:20:34,317 --> 00:20:36,360
如果超负荷
If there is a catastrophic overload.

353
00:20:36,444 --> 00:20:39,322
爆炸会毁掉整个飞船,
The full force of the explosion
will break up the Jumper,

