00:21:16,984 --> 00:21:18,486
还有23分钟
23 minutes.

363
00:21:23,991 --> 00:21:25,076
Weir博士?
Doctor Weir?

364
00:21:25,159 --> 00:21:26,369
对不起, 我现在没有时间
I'm sorry, I don't have time right now.

365
00:21:26,452 --> 00:21:29,038
这些人不是想拿回这艘飞船
Neither do those people that are trapped
aboard the ship of the ancestors.

366
00:21:29,914 --> 00:21:31,332
消息传得真快
News travels fast.

367
00:21:31,666 --> 00:21:34,502
当你们探险队员呼救的时候
我和她谈了
I was speaking with one of your expedition
members, when she was called in to help.

368
00:21:34,627 --> 00:21:37,171
好吧, 我应该知道我们没有时间了
Well then, you are aware that
we are very short on time.

369
00:21:37,296 --> 00:21:39,006
我知道
I am.

370
00:21:40,007 --> 00:21:42,009
但还是很重要
Still, this is important.

371
00:21:43,594 --> 00:21:44,554
好吧
Ok

372
00:21:45,513 --> 00:21:47,849
你不知道一件事
