死亡临近他们了
there is a ritual prayer that is said,
when one knows that death is upon them.

374
00:21:52,562 --> 00:21:53,813
我们不这么认为
We don't know that it is.

375
00:21:53,896 --> 00:21:55,273
有人告诉我这是不可避免的
I'm told that it is all but inevitable.

376
00:21:55,398 --> 00:21:56,107
谁说的?
By who?

377
00:21:56,607 --> 00:21:57,817
那不重要
It is not important.

378
