380
00:22:07,118 --> 00:22:10,746
只是个简单的仪式, 只需要一点时间....
It is a simple rite, but will not take more
than a few moments to....

381
00:22:10,830 --> 00:22:15,877
Hollan? 我们要劲我们全力来就他们
Hollan? We need to concentrate all of
our efforts on saving them.

382
00:22:15,960 --> 00:22:18,045
此时此刻Teyla自己的信念是什么?
At the risk of forsaking Teyla's own beliefs?

383
00:22:18,087 --> 00:22:21,716
重要的是我们要用我们现有很少的时间
尽我们最大的努力....
It is important that we use what
little time we have, to try everything....

384
00:22:21,757 --> 00:22:24,635
这件事上,
不用你告诉我什么重要什么不重要
I would ask you not to tell me what is important,
and what is not, in this case.

385
00:22:25,636 --> 00:22:28,139
- 对不起, 现在我没有时间聊天
- 为什么不行?
- I'm sorry, I can't have this conversation right now.
- Why not?

386
00:22:28,306 --> 00:22:29,807
因为我们在浪费时间
Because we are wasting time.

387
00:22:29,891 --> 00:22:31,517
这一时刻Teyla早就准备好了
This is time that Teyla can use to prepare.

388
00:22:31,601 --> 00:22:33,895
好了, 你认为死亡是必然的
Alright, you perceive death
a certain way.

389
00:22:34,020 --> 00:22:36,647
我也承认. I事实上, 我也尊重你们的想法
I accept that. In fact, I respect that.

390
00:22:36,939 --> 00:22:41,652
但是我们没有准备去死
我们必须尽力去避免死亡
