We do everything we can to stave it off.

391
00:22:41,777 --> 00:22:42,987
这才是我们应该做的
That is who we are.

392
00:22:43,070 --> 00:22:45,114
我并不想中止你的工作
I'm not asking you to suspend your efforts.

393
00:22:45,198 --> 00:22:48,034
你想让我告诉这飞船上所有人,
No. You want me to tell
everyone on that ship,

394
00:22:48,075 --> 00:22:49,535
他们最好还是安心等死?
that they should expect to die?

395
00:22:50,203 --> 00:22:51,913
我不会说的
I will not send them that message.

396
00:22:51,996 --> 00:22:57,001
并且如果你觉得这样侵犯了Teyla的权利,
我向你道歉
And if you feel that, that violates
Teyla's rights, I apologise.

397
00:22:57,168 --> 00:23:01,839
我会道歉的. 但是现在不是时候
我必须走了
I truly do. But there's nothing I can do
about that right now. I have to go.

398
00:23:15,269 --> 00:23:19,106
<i>很好. 现在我们手头上</i>
<i>有了所有探险者1号人员名单</i>
