<i>the Jumper manifest, already laid out here.</i>

399
00:23:19,190 --> 00:23:20,900
<i>你那里有什么可以利用的工具</i>
<i>What's your personal inventory.</i>

400
00:23:20,983 --> 00:23:24,362
我这有把瑞士军刀
Alright, from the vest,
we got a swiss army knife.

401
00:23:24,737 --> 00:23:30,451
一些巧克力, 还有点水
火柴, 急救包
Some chocolate, some water.
Matches, emergency kit.

402
00:23:30,952 --> 00:23:34,914
还有些酒精, 碘酒, 止疼片
We have alcohol, iodine, pain killers

403
00:23:35,039 --> 00:23:36,165
这是什么?
What is this?

404
00:23:37,166 --> 00:23:39,627
Teyla在飞船储藏室找到一个心脏起搏器
Teyla found a portable difibrillator
in the ships storage.

405
00:23:39,752 --> 00:23:43,256
我在想. 如果Sheppard少校被电击,
