I thought of that. If Major Sheppard received
the same electric shock, it would likely kill him.

406
00:23:43,256 --> 00:23:44,173
没错
Right

407
00:23:44,173 --> 00:23:46,342
什么都试试. 每次试一样
Try everything. One item at a time.

408
00:23:53,683 --> 00:23:54,433
Weir博士!
Dr Weir!

409
00:23:54,851 --> 00:23:56,727
Cavenaugh, 你是不是有什么新发现
Cavenaugh, I hope you've got
something to tell me.

410
00:23:56,853 --> 00:23:58,062
是的
Yes, I do.

411
00:23:58,813 --> 00:24:00,314
他妈的怎么回事?
What the hell was that?

412
00:24:00,982 --> 00:24:02,024
你说什么?
Excuse me?

413
00:24:02,316 --> 00:24:06,362
我很高兴离开SGC, 因为我,
因为我可以参军了,
I happily left the SGC, because I had,
had it up to here, with the military running things,

414
00:24:06,404 --> 00:24:08,406
你却不让我参与秘密研究
and you just busted me like a private.

415
00:24:08,531 --> 00:24:11,659
别总胡思乱想, 这没什么秘密
Don't be so dramatic, besides
the Air Force doesn't have privates.

416
00:24:12,034 --> 00:24:16,956
不止是我. 你撤掉了我整个研究小组的职务
Neither do I. You just cut them off.
Right in front of my research team.

417
00:24:17,039 --> 00:24:19,000
就为了这事? 你有什么不满吗?
That's what this is about? You're embarrassed?

418
00:24:19,083 --> 00:24:20,960
我承认确实有点丢人
Well humiliated would be a little more accurate.

419
00:24:21,002 --> 00:24:23,254
我顾及不到任何人的颜面
I haven't worked up to humiliation yet.

420
00:24:23,337 --> 00:24:28,384
我只是做了个假设,
只是做了一个普通市民应该做的
I just assumed, that with a civilian in charge of
the expedition, there would be a little bit more.

421
00:24:28,467 --> 00:24:31,929
我们已经不再是一个市民,
我们和地球隔绝了
A civilian is in charge,
and we are cut off from Earth.

422
00:24:31,971 --> 00:24:34,599
整个基地就好像一个大移民
Which makes Atlantis,
almost like a colony.

423
00:24:34,682 --> 00:24:35,766
我明白这点
I suppose.

424
00:24:35,850 --> 00:24:37,518
那好,
我是这里的主管
Well I'm governor of that colony.

425
00:24:37,643 --> 00:24:39,020
说得真好
Well that's all very well and good.

426
00:24:39,103 --> 00:24:40,688
你有什么异议吗?
Do you have a problem with that?

427
00:24:41,606 --> 00:24:42,732
你没明白我的意思
You're missing my point.

428
00:24:42,815 --> 00:24:44,275
不是, 是你没明白我的意思
No, you're missing mine.

429
00:24:44,984 --> 00:24:47,320
如果你再因为你的自私
If you waste one more minute,
which could be used

430
00:24:47,361 --> 00:24:51,485
浪费救出他们的宝贵的每1分钟,
to help the people trapped
on that ship, because of your ego?

431
00:24:51,490 --> 00:24:54,869
我保证我会把你送到一个孤星上,
I promise you, I will dial the co-ordinates
of a very lonely planet,

432
00:24:54,869 --> 00:24:57,496
在那里你永远是最主要的
where you can be as self important
as you wanna be.

