00:25:39,637 --> 00:25:41,347
Zalinka博士, 请接控制室
Dr Zalinka to control room.

440
00:25:42,140 --> 00:25:44,934
我有新发现了
I think I have something

441
00:25:47,520 --> 00:25:48,855
我们在接受信号
We're receiving.

442
00:25:50,398 --> 00:25:51,983
探险者1号, 我是Weir
Jumper One, this is Weir.

443
00:25:52,150 --> 00:25:53,860
Zelenka博士有新发现
Doctor Zelenka's come up with something.

444
00:25:53,985 --> 00:25:55,570
Zelenka. 为什么我总忘不掉你?
Zelenka. Why can I never
remember that name?

445
00:25:55,653 --> 00:25:59,616
<i>他已经找到了</i>
<i>飞船推进器的主控系统</i>
