I'm relaying the schematics to your data pad.

447
00:26:01,993 --> 00:26:03,912
太好了, 我们有救了
Thank you, now we're getting somewhere.

448
00:26:04,037 --> 00:26:04,579
什么?
What?

449
00:26:04,662 --> 00:26:07,081
