00:27:39,841 --> 00:27:41,134
没什么
Not much sir.

469
00:27:43,636 --> 00:27:45,138
还是没有反映
No reaction to alcohol.

470
00:27:46,264 --> 00:27:47,515
好吧, 下一个是什么?
Right, What next?

471
00:27:49,767 --> 00:27:52,228
医生没说洒点盐在这生物上吗?
Did the Doctor not say to pour salt
on the creature?

472
00:27:52,562 --> 00:27:57,150
我想这不用说. 你就试试所有的东西吧
I think that was a metaphor. But it doesn't matter.
Just try everything.

473
00:28:21,299 --> 00:28:23,801
水. 给我点水
Water. Give me water.

