I think the engine fired for a microsecond,
but it stopped.

488
00:29:40,170 --> 00:29:41,379
哦 不是吧
Oh no.

489
00:29:41,629 --> 00:29:42,630
怎么了?
What?

490
00:29:44,632 --> 00:29:45,633
怎么了?
What?

