00:30:32,138 --> 00:30:35,141
McKay博士, 还是希望我们能及时收回推进器
Dr McKay, is still hopeful we can retract
the drive pod in time.

502
00:30:43,733 --> 00:30:44,901
明白了
Understood.

503
00:30:47,028 --> 00:30:49,989
我们现在没有任何新进展
但是时间不多了
We haven't come up with anything yet.
But there's still time.

504
00:30:50,448 --> 00:30:51,783
明白
Yes ma'am.

505
00:30:52,534 --> 00:30:53,910
Sheppard少校怎么样了?
How is Major Sheppard?

506
00:30:54,077 --> 00:30:55,370
我还活着
I'm still here.

507
00:30:56,496 --> 00:30:59,833
<i>坚持住</i>
<i>我们还在研究</i>
<i>Hang in there Major. </i>
<i>We're working on the problem.</i>

508
00:30:59,833 --> 00:31:01,251
我知道你们在努力
I know you are.

509
00:31:03,419 --> 00:31:08,550
听着, 我想在我还能说话的时候说几句想说的
Listen, I'd like to say something,
while I still can.

510
00:31:08,716 --> 00:31:11,344
不要! 你会没事的
Don't! You're gonna get through this.

511
00:31:15,932 --> 00:31:21,187
他不会让我死的
If I was. He wouldn't have let me go.

512
00:31:21,771 --> 00:31:23,439
谁不会让你死?
Who wouldn't have let you go?

513
00:31:26,442 --> 00:31:28,319
幽灵们
The Wraith.

514
00:31:52,135 --> 00:31:56,055
我才他没有杀我,
是因为在他眼里我这样比死了更好
I guess he saw me as good as dead,
cos he just walked away.

515
00:31:56,598 --> 00:31:59,726
所以, 我想说的是....
So, what I wanted to say was....

516
00:31:59,767 --> 00:32:02,187
留着力气等回来和我说
Save your strength John.
And tell me in person.

517
00:32:02,645 --> 00:32:04,147
这很重要
This is important.

518
00:32:07,233 --> 00:32:08,651
我在听
I'm listening.

519
00:32:10,904 --> 00:32:12,655
我们能把他送回基地
We should sent him through the event horizon.

520
00:32:13,072 --> 00:32:16,659
如果McKay博士及时解决了问题,
我们就让少校赶紧回去
If Doctor McKay figures it out in time,
we can fix the Major up on the other side.

521
00:32:16,743 --> 00:32:18,286
如果他不行了, 我们也都死
If he doesn't, we're all dead anyway.

522
00:32:18,328 --> 00:32:19,496
不要给我压力
No pressure.

523
00:32:21,498 --> 00:32:24,250
Sheppard少校不要那么急躁
Major Sheppard would effectively be in suspended
animation for the entire time.

524
00:32:24,375 --> 00:32:26,002
- 我们不能冒这个险
- 为什么不行?
- We can't risk that.
- Why not?

525
00:32:26,085 --> 00:32:28,421
如果这个生物对水有反映,
If the creature reacted that violently
to drops of water,

526
00:32:28,546 --> 00:32:30,507
谁也不知道它对时空门有没有什么反映
who knows how it would react
to Stargate travel.

527
00:32:30,798 --> 00:32:33,718
你的意思是说,
只要教授身上有这东西他就不能过时空门?
Are you telling me Major Sheppard can't come
through the gate, while that thing is on him?

528
00:32:33,927 --> 00:32:35,803
那么我们现在必须抓紧了!
Then we must do something now!

529
00:32:44,896 --> 00:32:46,981
用起搏器杀了我
Hit me with the defibrillator.

530
00:32:52,111 --> 00:32:54,072
少校你一定是想到什么了
You may be onto something Major.

531
00:32:54,322 --> 00:32:56,199
你说过他可能会死的
You said that might kill him.

532
00:32:56,658 --> 00:32:58,284
我们就是这么想的
That's the idea.

533
00:32:58,409 --> 00:32:59,619
我不明白
I don't understand.

534
00:32:59,744 --> 00:33:02,956
Teyla. 你说过这生物和幽灵差不多
Teyla. You said this creature was like a Wraith.

535
00:33:03,081 --> 00:33:03,790
是的
Yes.

536
00:33:03,832 --> 00:33:06,459
那么你试想一下
如果上帝让少校死, 他们会怎么做,
Then how do you think it would respond,
if God forbit,

537
00:33:06,584 --> 00:33:08,628
Sheppard少校那上死掉, 那么...
Major Sheppard were to die right now, then.

538
00:33:11,881 --> 00:33:13,591
它就不再附着少校了
It would stop feeding.

539
00:33:13,758 --> 00:33:15,260
没错. 幽灵就会这样
Exactly. Just as a Wraith would.

540
00:33:15,510 --> 00:33:16,886
你们到底是怎么想的?
How is that an idea?

541
00:33:17,053 --> 00:33:20,014
我们只是想欺骗这个生物
它的寄生体已经死了
I'm suggesting that we fool the creature into
thinking that its prey's dead,

542
00:33:20,056 --> 00:33:21,636
所以我们必须让少校停止心跳
by stopping the Major's heart.

543
00:33:21,641 --> 00:33:24,060
如果想法没错. 它会离开少校的
If I'm right. It should let him go.

544
00:33:24,060 --> 00:33:26,646
一旦生物离开
我们就再击一次让少校苏醒
If that thing let's go.
We give him another jolt.

545
00:33:26,938 --> 00:33:29,858
试一下. 如果不行,
就把他扔进时空门
Give it a try. If it doesn't work,
send him through the event horizon.

546
00:33:30,066 --> 00:33:32,026
他会暂时呆在那
He'll keep there,
as good as the deep freeze.

547
00:33:38,783 --> 00:33:40,869
John, 你确定你要这么做么?
John, are you sure you wanna do this?

548
00:33:41,286 --> 00:33:43,037
我真的很想把这该死的东西除掉
I want this damn thing off me.

549
00:33:45,415 --> 00:33:47,125
准备对探险者1号进行急救
Be prepared for a code blue in the Jumper bay.

550
00:33:47,292 --> 00:33:49,294
Ford少尉, 你知道怎么做吧?
Lt Ford, do you know how to do this?

551
00:33:49,586 --> 00:33:52,130
- 是的. 把他衣服割开
- 什么?
- Yes sir. Cut his shirt off.
- What?

552
00:33:52,213 --> 00:33:54,090
把他衣服割开!
Cut his shirt off!

553
00:34:01,181 --> 00:34:02,557
200幅. 把他的饰物那开
Charging 200. Move his tags.

554
00:34:04,058 --> 00:34:05,727
- 什么?
- 那开里面的胸牌
- What?
- Move his chain, inside.

555
00:34:05,768 --> 00:34:07,562
在表面擦点油
Place the lubrication,right on the paddles.

556
00:34:07,937 --> 00:34:10,023
准备好了
Ready to go.

557
00:34:13,359 --> 00:34:17,280
一旦这虫子掉下来我一定杀了它
Once the bug falls off, I'm gonna have to kill it.

558
00:34:17,780 --> 00:34:19,949
准备下一次,
然后我们再帮你苏醒
Ready to charge up again,
and we'll hit it with another jolt.

559
00:34:20,116 --> 00:34:24,662
McKay, 如果我们第一下不成功,
我们必须再次打开那舱门.
McKay, if we can't restart his heart on the first try,
we'll need that bulkhead door open again.

560
00:34:25,538 --> 00:34:26,706
好的
Done.

561
00:34:28,208 --> 00:34:29,959
我们其中一个必须带他过去
One of us is gonna have to get him through.

562
00:34:30,001 --> 00:34:31,252
我来
I will.

563
00:34:41,221 --> 00:34:42,680
开始吧!
Do it!

564
00:34:48,645 --> 00:34:49,938
没有心跳!
No pulse!

565
00:34:56,027 --> 00:34:57,320
下不来
It won't come off.

566
00:34:57,946 --> 00:35:02,116
冷静. 也许需要一段时间
Settle. It may take a moment.

567
00:35:06,704 --> 00:35:07,872
少尉?
Lieutenant?

568
00:35:45,869 --> 00:35:47,203
没反映?
Nothing?

569
00:35:47,829 --> 00:35:49,622
没反映! 快带他过去
Nothing! Let's get him through.

570
00:35:59,632 --> 00:36:02,135
- 好了?
- 是的
- Got him?
- Yes.

571
00:36:05,680 --> 00:36:09,267
我是Ford少尉. 那个生物已经取下来了
This is Lt Ford. The creature has been
sucessfully removed from Major Sheppard,

572
00:36:09,309 --> 00:36:14,022
但是我们无法让他苏醒. 他和Teyla,
现在在时空门的另一端
but we were unable to revive him. Both he and Teyla,
are now on the other side of the event horizon.

573
00:36:16,149 --> 00:36:21,070
谢谢你Rodney少尉, 你们还有7分钟
Thank you Lt. Rodney, you have seven minutes.

574
00:36:45,386 --> 00:36:48,389
我只解决了一部分,
但是我们快没时间了. 我们可能做不到了
I'm only halfway through the possible circuit pathways,
and times almost up. We're not gonna make it.

575
00:36:48,431 --> 00:36:49,933
你就做吧. 现在还有时间
Just keep on it. There's still time.

576
00:36:50,016 --> 00:36:51,851
你应该进时空门里面
You should consider stepping
into the event horizon.

577
00:36:51,851 --> 00:36:52,894
我是认真的
I'm serious.

578
00:36:52,977 --> 00:36:55,522
我会坚持到最后的, 但是给你个选择,
最好还是离开
I'll keep trying till the end, but given your choices,
that's a far better way to go.

579
00:36:56,022 --> 00:36:58,233
把你一个人留在这个危险的地方?
Leave you here alone with that thing
wrapped up in my jacket?

580
00:36:58,441 --> 00:37:00,193
你确定那东西死了
- 肯定死了
You did check to make sure it was dead.
- It's dead.

581
00:37:00,276 --> 00:37:02,821
很好, 因为爆炸性减压, 然后窒息死亡, 是很有可能....
Good, because explosive decompression, and death
by suffocation with that thing, is possibly....

582
00:37:02,946 --> 00:37:04,447
- 干你的活!
- 对不起
- Work!
- I'm sorry

583
00:37:09,452 --> 00:37:10,411
还有多久?
Time?

584
00:37:10,703 --> 00:37:12,163
2分20秒
2 minutes 20 seconds.

585
00:37:12,372 --> 00:37:13,998
Rodney, 又过了2分钟
Rodney, we're down to 2 minutes

586
00:37:14,165 --> 00:37:16,793
我知道时间. 我现在还有2打线路没有试
I know the time. I've still got over two dozen
circuits I haven't tried.

587
00:37:17,710 --> 00:37:19,629
不用按照顺序来. 随意试哪一个
Don't be so methodical. Just pick one at random.

588
00:37:19,754 --> 00:37:22,048
如果那么做, 那样的话我就同时运行了2个系统
If I do that, I run the risk of attempting to
activate the same circuit twice.

589
00:37:22,048 --> 00:37:22,924
试试吧!
Just try!

590
00:37:23,091 --> 00:37:24,592
我告诉你, 那根本不可能....
I'm telling you, there's no way I could....

591
00:37:27,637 --> 00:37:28,721
等等
Wait.

592
00:37:38,231 --> 00:37:39,649
我想我成功了
I think I did it.

593
00:37:44,237 --> 00:37:47,448
Elizabeth?
我估计推进器收回了
Elizabeth?
I think the engine pods retracted.

594
00:37:59,252 --> 00:38:00,753
为什么还是看不到你们?
Why haven't you shown up?

595
00:38:05,925 --> 00:38:07,635
对啊. 为什么我们还是不动?
She's right. Why aren't we moving?

596
00:38:09,429 --> 00:38:12,098
是惯性. 飞船是靠惯性穿过时空门的
It's inertia. The drive shift end went
through the Stargate.

597
00:38:12,223 --> 00:38:13,850
我们有没有任何前进的动力了
We've shed all our forward momentum.

598
00:38:17,979 --> 00:38:21,274
你再浪费时间. 任何一个力,
都会给予一个相同的反力
You're wasting your time. For every action,
there is an equal and opposite reaction.

599
00:38:22,650 --> 00:38:24,152
那么我们该怎么办?
Then what are we gonna do?

600
00:38:31,701 --> 00:38:33,203
还有一分钟
One minute.

601
00:38:36,206 --> 00:38:39,501
后舱. 让后舱爆炸
The rear hatch. Blow the rear hatch.

602
00:38:39,667 --> 00:38:41,544
那么就有足够的力让怎么穿过去了
It should give you enough thrust
to make it through.

603
00:38:41,753 --> 00:38:44,088
可以这么做. 但是只有一个机器可以引爆
I can do it. But the only mechanism
to blow the hatch is back here.

604
00:38:51,054 --> 00:38:55,141
我来. 没时间了. 快走!
I'll do it. There's no time. Just go!

605
00:38:57,644 --> 00:38:58,937
30秒
30 seconds.

606
00:39:51,281 --> 00:39:52,740
我去通道
I'll be in the Jumper bay.

607
00:40:01,374 --> 00:40:02,625
再来一次!
Again!

608
00:40:10,800 --> 00:40:12,177
他会没事的
He's gonna be fine.

609
00:40:33,406 --> 00:40:34,782
干得不错Rodney
Well done Rodney.

610
00:40:34,949 --> 00:40:35,783
看着吧
We'll see.

611
00:40:39,120 --> 00:40:40,455
有脉搏了
We've got a pulse.

612
00:40:47,420 --> 00:40:48,922
心跳越来越强了
It's getting stronger.

613
00:40:55,220 --> 00:40:56,596
他很快就没事了
He's going to be ok.

614
00:41:36,135 --> 00:41:37,053
感觉如何?
How are you feeling?

615
00:41:37,178 --> 00:41:38,096
饿
Starving.

616
00:41:38,429 --> 00:41:42,600
他可弄了不少吻痕, 但是Beckett医生说
他几天就好
He's got quite the hickey, but Dr Beckett says
he'll be fine in a few days.

617
00:41:43,518 --> 00:41:44,686
你需要休息
We should let you rest.

618
00:41:44,727 --> 00:41:45,979
不, 你应该给我点吃的
No, you should get me food.

619
00:41:46,062 --> 00:41:47,647
我想可以安排
I think we can arrange that.

620
00:41:47,814 --> 00:41:49,149
早日康复
Welcome back sir.

621
00:41:49,232 --> 00:41:51,526
这真是个奇迹
I must admit, it is a pleasant surprise.

622
00:41:51,985 --> 00:41:54,779
顺便说一下. 你上次想说什么?
By the way. What were you gonna say?

623
00:41:55,155 --> 00:41:55,864
什么时候?
When?

624
00:41:56,030 --> 00:41:59,617
在你认为... 你知道的
Before, when you thought... ou know

625
00:42:01,119 --> 00:42:02,162
哦 那件事啊
Oh that.

626
00:42:02,162 --> 00:42:06,082
那时候我没让你说
但是现在我想知道
I didn't want you to say at the time.
But now I'm curious.

627
00:42:07,125 --> 00:42:08,418
我那时候想说...
I was gonna say...

628
00:42:15,425 --> 00:42:17,093
你们大家要互相照顾
Take care of each other.

629
00:42:19,512 --> 00:42:20,638
不错
That's nice.

630
00:42:21,472 --> 00:42:24,142
我们也是这么做的
And indeed we did.

631
00:42:24,184 --> 00:42:27,770
是的你做到了. 再次感谢
Yes you did. Thank you, again.

632
00:42:27,770 --> 00:42:28,980
没什么
You're welcome.

633
00:42:29,147 --> 00:42:30,231
晚安
Goodnight.

634
00:42:36,654 --> 00:42:39,407
你一定不是想说那句话,
对吧?
You weren't really gonna say that,
were you?

635
00:42:40,283 --> 00:42:42,911
我不知道你想说什么
I have no idea what you're talking about.

636
00:42:43,953 --> 00:42:45,663
你一定知道


I didn't think so.

